To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MomersionIndicator _momersion;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_momersion = MOMERSION(symbol, minPeriod, fullPeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_momersion.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "momersionindicator", _momersion.Current.Value);
}
